name: CheerUp
0:
”Alexa, launch Cheer Up.”
”Alexa, open Cheer Up and say something nice.”
”Alexa, ask Cheer Up to say something to make me feel better.”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: cheer up
des: Are you ever feeling down and wish you could talk to someone? Maybe you need some advice or just a nice comment. In that case, "Cheer Up!" is ready to tell you that life isn't that bad and that finding lost chocolate around the house is a good idea. Just ask Alexa to cheer you up and mull over her fun quips and honest advice.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
